instance-variables.Text: "Whoa! You could've killed some of us! We're fine-tuning the thorn resistance device from Father H on our shields for some of the more, you know, sensitive explorers. So please, move along." - V
"How do you think she got the bridge to break? She might have panicked and broken something. All those girly emotions, you know? Hahaha!"
"Aw, come on, we don't mean it. Can't you take a joke?"
Just typical V and his friends, I guess. Always the favored one. Always the jerk.
Hmm. This bridge ahead doesn't seem awfully well-maintained.
The sign reads: "A convenience for all the promising young men who come after me. So you can start getting some real exploration done! Signed, O"
